{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The free version of Ghostbane, Ghostbane: Prologue to experience the core gameplay and get a taste of what's to come in the full version. Don't forget to add it to your wishlist!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;<strong>Ghostbane: Prologue</strong>&quot; is a multiplayer horror game that you can play with your friends. Detect paranormal activity, collect evidence of ghosts, hunt ghosts by rituals, and conduct detailed investigations about ghosts in your main base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/extras/event_1.gif?t=1733824538\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/extras/header_1.png?t=1733824538\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go to the area of paranormal activity. Use the unique Ghostbane equipment to identify the type of ghost. Ritualise the area to capture the identified ghost and hunt it with the ritual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/extras/rituel_gif.gif?t=1733824538\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/extras/header_2.png?t=1733824538\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is an experience that will push your horror limits. We've prepared it with carefully designed unique scenes and superior graphics. Meticulously crafted environments and eerie details will draw you into the atmosphere. You will feel tension in your bones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/extras/capsule_gif.gif?t=1733824538\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/extras/header_3.png?t=1733824538\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ghosts captured as a result of paranormal research and hunting activities can be observed in capsules at your main base. These capsules allow you to analyse a ghost's history, personality, manner of death and relationship to paranormal activity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/extras/item_gif.gif?t=1733824538\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733824538","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733824538","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/9db241b951b8f3bffe428b61105f620b5ceaa295/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733824538","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962750/9db241b951b8f3bffe428b61105f620b5ceaa295/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733824538","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The free version of Ghostbane, Ghostbane: Prologue to experience the core gameplay and get a taste of what's to come in the full version. Don't forget to add it to your wishlist!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;<strong>Ghostbane: Prologue</strong>&quot; is a multiplayer horror game that you can play with your friends. Detect paranormal activity, co